Write HCL code for Stat, generating the 4 status codes SAOK, SADR,
SINS and SHLT(see Figure 4.26).


 word Stat = [
	 imem_error || dmem_error : SADR;		# Instruction memory or data memory errer.
	 !instr_valid : SINS;					# Invalid instruction code.
	 icode == IHALT : SHLT					# Halt by the halt icode signal.
	 1 : SAOK;								# Normal case.
 ];
